body:
Test case built from reading the very colorful, highly reflective, gomega packages:

```
func TestCallInterfaceValue(t *testing.T) {                                                   
        type Done <-chan interface{}
        var ch interface{} = make(Done)                                                       
        
        f := func(done <-chan interface{}) {}                                                 
        
        v := ValueOf(f)
        v.Call([]Value{ValueOf(ch)})                                                          
}                                                                                             
```
